{"tid":1003750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"花豹1隻打趴100人類　襲村狠咬拖爬傷鄉民","createTime":"2019-02-01T02:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T03:15:32.000Z","uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b76b99ff66a4c3fdb59a6bd5838c821afe837edf","tid":1003750,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:11:03.000Z","msg":"印度賈朗達爾市(Jalandhar)在今日發生一起花豹誤闖村莊，並與人類發生衝突的事件，影片更清楚拍到，花豹1隻打趴逾100人類，牠更一度被逼急，對鄉民狠咬、拖、爬，傳出有6人因此受傷。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，這隻花豹似乎與人類爭地，最先有民眾發現這隻花豹躲在一處民宅裡，通報當局後，全村展開大追捕。但花豹一度被逼急，在面對上百位民眾的圍攻下，花豹只好展開攻擊模式，1個打100個，並在人群中見人就攻擊，村裡也因此上演「全員逃走中」，有多位鄉民遭到花豹咬、拖、拉、爬，傳出至少有6人受傷，但未有人因此受重傷或死亡。據悉當局試圖對花豹吹箭麻醉，但失敗，只好進行地毯式搜索追捕。<br />\n <br />\n目前未知這隻花豹是否已被順利「逮捕」，而當局計畫捕獲花豹後，會將牠送回野外。"},{"pid":"ed1f5ca888352650743cf1e9cb756e6d7f877b9b","tid":1003750,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:15:38.000Z","msg":"虎將 要改口做  豹將"},{"pid":"4387b71c140bb9bfcb251d154b643e0dd274ee29","tid":1003750,"uid":36035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff4e3b8eb03b72de9fef75ee0ab84acc2c46da70","tid":1003750,"uid":93986,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jXr6Cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jXr6Cb.png&h=0805f787&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0da6ff6f123867c7c6105c41d21569022f416f2","tid":1003750,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T02:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s1.sinaimg.cn/middle/69f84565xb604c5d0c6f0&amp;690\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.sinaimg.cn%2Fmiddle%2F69f84565xb604c5d0c6f0%26690&h=43d7c2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前新聞相 點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0b8878db943780d46fedcea513580b87ac8f51","tid":1003750,"uid":13700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c